ActCanada Pension Plan Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of JOHN S. MONTALBANO of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, in the place of Pierre Choquette, effective February 13, 2017.
